pageContext.claim: “With a brand new USMCA and the USMCA is expected to create 76,000 new automotive jobs for the first time in five years and that's going to be also great. pageContext.analysis: This is a White House estimate, but such jobs estimates are generally never credible and rarely come to fruition.
